modules.description: This module provides utilities for manipulating OCaml ASTs by attaching metadata to labels and types, supporting operations like documentation annotation, versioning, and environment configuration. It works with Ppxlib AST nodes such as `label_declaration`, `type_declaration`, and `expression`, enabling code generation for command-line interfaces via constructs like expressions and structures. Targeted at PPX extensions, it facilitates tasks like automatic CLI component creation using Cmdliner and enriching AST nodes with declarative metadata during preprocessing.
